flights_fit <- rpart(
  formula = late_departure ~ ., 
  data = flights_train, 
  method = 'class'
)

rpart.plot(flights_fit, 
           yesno = 2, 
           fallen.leaves = TRUE, 
           faclen = 2, 
           digits = 4)

flights_test_pred <- flights_test %>%
  add_predictions(flights_fit, type = 'class')

conf_mat <- flights_test_pred %>%
              conf_mat(truth = late_departure, estimate = pred)
